<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{audit.title}} 결과보고서</title>
<style>
  body{font-family:'맑은 고딕',Arial,sans-serif;font-size:10pt;margin:20mm;color:#172B4D}
  h1{font-size:16pt;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;margin-bottom:4pt;color:#172B4D}
  h2{font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;margin-top:16pt;margin-bottom:4pt;color:#1a2332;border-bottom:1pt solid #1a2332;padding-bottom:3pt}
  table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:10pt}
  th{background:#1a2332;color:#fff;padding:5pt 6pt;font-size:9pt;text-align:left}
  td{border:0.5pt solid #ccc;padding:5pt 6pt;font-size:9pt;vertical-align:top}
  .sum-table td:first-child{font-weight:bold;background:#f0f4f8;width:30%}
  .result{font-weight:bold;padding:2pt 6pt;border-radius:3pt;display:inline-block}
  .ok{color:#1a7c3e;background:#eafaf1}
  .ng{color:#c0392b;background:#fdecea}
  .na{color:#7f8c8d;background:#f4f4f4}
  .obs{color:#e67e22;background:#fef5e7}
  .footer{font-size:8pt;color:#888;text-align:right;margin-top:20pt;border-top:0.5pt solid #ccc;padding-top:6pt}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>심사 점검표 결과보고서</h1>
<table class="sum-table">
  <tr><td>심사명</td><td>{{audit.title}}</td><td>심사일</td><td>{{audit.date}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>심사원</td><td>{{audit.auditor}}</td><td>피심사 부서</td><td>{{audit.dept}}</td></tr>
  <tr><td>전체 항목</td><td>{{summary.total}}건</td><td>작성일</td><td>{{generated.date}}</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>심사 결과 요약</h2>
<table>
  <tr><th>구분</th><th>건수</th><th>비율</th><th>비고</th></tr>
  {{summary.rows}}
  <tr><td><strong>합계</strong></td><td>{{summary.total}}건</td><td>100%</td><td></td></tr>
</table>

{{sections}}

{{ng.section}}

<div class="footer">Generated by 심사 점검표 앱 · {{generated.datetime}}</div>
</body>
</html>
